import React from 'react'
import { View, Text, TouchableOpacity, StyleSheet, Image} from 'react-native'

import {icons} from '../constants/icons'

export default function homeScreenButtons({buttonVals}) {
      return (
            <View>
                  <TouchableOpacity>
                        <Image source={require(buttonVals[0].img)}/>
                        <Text>{buttonVals[0].title}</Text>
                  </TouchableOpacity>
                  <TouchableOpacity>
                        <Image source={require(buttonVals[1].img)}/>
                        <Text>{buttonVals[1].title}</Text>
                  </TouchableOpacity>
                  <TouchableOpacity>
                        <Image source={require(buttonVals[2].img)}/>
                        <Text>{buttonVals[2].title}</Text>
                  </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>
      )
}
